  "title": "AB03 - Operations Assistant Manager [Deployment & Reporting]",
  "description": "<p><strong>Operations Assistant Manager [Deployment & Reporting]</strong></p><p><strong>Salary:</strong> $2,800 - $3,200</p><p><strong>Location: </strong>Tiong Bahru / WFH</p><p><strong>Working Days: </strong>5 weekdays (3 weekdays & 2 weekends)</p><p><strong>Working Hour:</strong></p><p>Weekdays: 10.20am - 7.20pm [On-site]</p><p>Weekend: 7.00am – 5pm [WFH]</p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><p><strong>Teachers & CSO Deployment</strong></p><ul><li>Plan and manage relief processes across branches for Teachers & Customer Service Officers -Track Attendance of Teachers & Customer Service Officers</li><li>Develop communications packages for teachers (e.g. Infographics, etc)</li><li>Design simple collaterals in accordance with brand marketing guidelines</li><li>Assist with scheduling and tracking of teacher assessments, appraisal, etc</li></ul><p><strong>Data-tracking & Manpower Resource Management</strong></p><ul><li>Plan and manage relief processes across branches for Teachers & CSOS</li><li>Oversee Teacher Allocation across all branches</li><li>Measure adherence to leave policies and implement measures to encourage adherence Manage relief data sheets</li><li>Deliver monthly report on key data points tracked by team</li></ul><p><strong>Oversee Relief Roster</strong></p><ul><li>Find relief teachers</li><li>Consolidate a list of relief, freelance relief classes taken monthly and inform HR</li></ul><p><strong>Assist with forecasting of recruitment needs of the following groups of teachers:</strong></p><ul><li>Relief, Adjunct, Part-time and Freelance</li></ul><p><strong>Data-tracking for Operations</strong></p><ul><li>Manage key data sheets for Operations needs</li><li>Deliver monthly report on key data points tracked by team</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirement:</strong></p><ul><li>At least Degree / Diploma in any discipline</li><li>Possess relevant experience</li><li>Proficiency in MS Office, Zoom, Google Drive</li></ul><p><strong>If you are keen to apply, please send me your resume and job applied for on WhatsApp at 8093 8699 or email me at anabel.thesupreme@gmail.com (˶ᵔ ᵕ ᵔ˶)</strong></p><p>❄️Anabel Boon Xue Qi | Consultant Associate (R25159272) |📍The Supreme HR Advisory EA No: 14C7279</p>",
